Output: a per-method r@20 / r@30 table on the 6 benchmark subjects,
versus the C5 baseline `788406=0.263 / 790322=0.289 / 755252=0.095 /
767022=0.117 / 767018=0.315 / 782149=0`. Anything that beats C5 on
